OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will seek to regain
OL,7,Fcontrol of the political agenda on
OL,8,FThursday with a series of
OL,9,Fannouncements on the cost of living
OL,10,Fand giving power to local communities.
OL,12,FWestminster remains focused on the
OL,13,FMakerfield by-election, now confirmed
OL,14,Ffor June 18, and the possibility of a
OL,15,Fleadership challenge by Greater
OL,16,FManchester mayor Andy Burnham.
OL,18,FAllies of Mr Burnham have suggested he
OL,19,Fmay not launch a bid for the top job
OL,20,Fimmediately if he returns to
OL,21,FWestminster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
