OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779325397
OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FLabour deputy leader Lucy Powell, who
OL,7,Fsupported his previous bid to fight a
OL,8,Fby-election in Gorton and Denton, told
OL,9,FLBC she did not "expect that's what
OL,10,FAndy's coming in to do".
OL,12,FBut a contest is widely expected after
OL,13,FMr Burnham's call for a "new path" and
OL,14,Fpromise to "change Labour".
