OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FThat expectation has led to
OL,7,Fspeculation over what policies the
OL,8,Fmayor would pursue in Downing Street,
OL,9,Fincluding reports he could continue
OL,10,Fwith Home Secretary Shabana Mahmood's
OL,11,Fplan to significantly extend the time
OL,12,Fimmigrants must wait to receive
OL,13,Fpermanent residency.
OL,15,FMr Burnham's team would not comment on
OL,16,Freports in the Guardian that he would
OL,17,Fsupport the proposal to increase the
OL,18,Fwait for indefinite leave to remain
OL,19,Ffrom five years to between 10 and 20
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
