OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FAway from the by-election, ministers
OL,7,Fwill seek to move on from speculation
OL,8,Fabout Sir Keir's future with a focus
OL,9,Fon policy.
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves is expected
OL,12,Fto announce plans to cut tariffs on
OL,13,Fsome food products in order to
OL,14,Fmitigate the impact of the Iran war.
OL,16,FShe will also announce the
OL,17,Fintroduction of free bus travel for
OL,18,Fchildren during August, after the
OL,19,FGovernment's decision to postpone a
OL,20,Frise in fuel duty planned for
OL,21,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
