OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed will
OL,7,Falso use a speech on Thursday to set
OL,8,Fout proposals to give local
OL,9,Fcommunities more power over their
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FHis proposals include minimum
OL,13,Fstandards for services such as pothole
OL,14,Frepairs and street cleaning, and
OL,15,Fpowers to limit the number of vape
OL,16,Fshops and gambling businesses on high
OL,17,Fstreets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
