OL,3,CStarmer seeks to regain initiative
OL,4,Camid Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FMeanwhile, campaigning will continue
OL,7,Fin Makerfield, where Mr Burnham faces
OL,8,FReform UK's Robert Kenyon, who
OL,9,Fcontested the seat in 2024, and
OL,10,FConservative Michael Winstanley, who
OL,11,Flast stood in the constituency in 1997.
OL,13,FThe Green Party and the Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrats are yet to announce their
OL,15,Fcandidates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
